divs: Sighting DetailsWas trying to get to sleep and staring out the window. It was dark out but the sun was almost coming up. All of a sudden something in the sky started emmiting a very bright light. The object appeared to be dark surrounded by bright white light. I am not sure how far away it was. Partialy obstructed by some leaves at the top of a tree. The light was turning some of the leaves white. It remained still the whole time. No sound. I was startled enough to grab for my camera but when I did that the light disappeared. Only lasted about 5-8 seconds.
Summary: Bright white glow appeared in sky, Made some leaves at the top of a tree look white. Possibly dark object in center, remained still.
